### 1. 전체 허브 목록 조회 (기본)
GET http://localhost:8086/api/v1/hubs/search
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

### 2. 허브명(hubName)으로 검색
GET http://localhost:8086/api/v1/hubs/search?hubName=서울
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json


### 3. 허브 주소(hubAddress)로 검색
GET http://localhost:8086/api/v1/hubs/search?hubAddress=청주
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json


### 4. 이름 + 주소 복합 검색
GET http://localhost:8086/api/v1/hubs/search?hubName=서울&hubAddress=송파
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json


### 5. 허브명 내림차순 정렬
GET http://localhost:8086/api/v1/hubs/search?sort=hubName,desc
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json


### 6. 검색 결과 없음 테스트
GET http://localhost:8086/api/v1/hubs/search?hubAddress=아무주소도없음
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json